                "url": "/topics/regulate"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/hajoon_chang_694437",
        "quote": "What free-market economists are not telling us is that the politics they want to get rid of are none other than those of democracy itself. When they say we need to insulate economic policies from politics, they are in effect advocating the castration of democracy.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Ha-Joon Chang",
            "url": "/quotes/hajoon_chang_694437"
        },
        "topics": [
            {
                "name": "Politics",
                "url": "/topics/politics"
