        "url": "/quotes/hajoon_chang_694427",
        "quote": "Imagine if all those kings and dukes hadn't commissioned those crazy cathedrals, paintings and music... we'd still be living in sticks and mud. Because none of those things made any economic sense. Human beings' capacity to 'waste time' is a miracle - but that's exactly what art is for.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Ha-Joon Chang",
            "url": "/quotes/hajoon_chang_694427"
        },
