    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/hajoon_chang_694430",
        "quote": "Basically, the myth is that America has been founded on the free market; the government has done very little; it has thrived under free trade. But actually, if you look at the history, this is actually the country that has succeeded most with protectionist policies.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Ha-Joon Chang",
            "url": "/quotes/hajoon_chang_694430"
        },
        "topics": [
